{"descriptions":[{"id":1308,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe suffixes \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་\u003c/span\u003e are associated only with the present-future form of the verb:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཞུ་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e but not *\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཞུས་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཟ་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e but not *\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབཟས་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབལྟ་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e but not *\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབལྟས་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe suffix \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་\u003c/span\u003e, which is sometimes spelled \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡས་\u003c/span\u003e, does not occur in Literary Tibetan, which instead uses the nominalizer \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔ་\u003c/span\u003e. The form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་\u003c/span\u003e, on the other hand, is used both in Spoken Tibetan and in the literary language.\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:29 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:29 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}